description:
The Alex Jones Show

Thursday January 15, 2009.

Austin businessman, North American Union researcher, and host of the one hour cable access program Simpe Truth, Bob Dacy, rides shotgun with Jason Bermas. Guests include Jack McLamb, the most highly decorated police officer in Phoenix history and host of the Jack McLamb radio show, and Russell Wood of the Property Rights Congress in Missouri. 

Hour-1: News and Open Lines
Hour-2: News and Open Lines
Hour-3: Open lines then Jack McLamb
Hour-4: Russell Wood then open lines
